data.description: This pristine 1-story home in the over-55 community of Hill Country retreat is move-in ready, and backs to a greenbelt! Featuring an open floor plan with hardwood flooring, crown molding, a spacious living room and open kitchen with breakfast bar, granite counters, stainless steel appliances including a gas range and dining nook with backyard access, home office/flex space, inside laundry room, primary bedroom with backyard views and bath with an extra-large walk-in shower and separate vanities. Enjoy the serene treetop and big sky views from the extended back patio, ready for entertaining or relaxing. The home is conveniently located nearby schools, parks and community amenities, and provides easy access to 1604, shopping and more. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your next home, book your personal tour today!
